_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     The package performs to draw the popular graphics of the MIRT in R
     environment.

_D_e_t_a_i_l_s:


       Package:  MIRT
       Type:     Package
       Version:  1.0
       Date:     2009-04-20
       License:  GPL verson 2 or newer

     Function list of this package: "MIRT"
      "vector.plot"
      "surface.2D"
      "surface.3D"
      "contour.plot"
      "difsurface.2D"
      "difsurface.3D"
      "centroid.plot"
      "clamshell.plot"
